flowchart TD
  B[Baseline] --> S[Stable]
  S --> T[Trusted]
  T --> A[Adaptive]
  A --> U[Autonomous]

  S -. rollback .-> B
  T -. rollback .-> S
  A -. rollback .-> T
  U -. rollback .-> A

  S --> GS{Gate checks pass?}
  T --> GT{Gate checks pass?}
  A --> GA{Gate checks pass?}

  GS -->|yes| T
  GS -->|no| RB1[Auto-freeze and rollback]
  GT -->|yes| A
  GT -->|no| RB2[Auto-freeze and rollback]
  GA -->|yes| U
  GA -->|no| RB3[Auto-freeze and rollback]

  RB1 --> B
  RB2 --> S
  RB3 --> T

  HC1[Human checkpoint\nOps + Safety + Personality] --> GS
  HC2[Human checkpoint\nOps + Safety + Personality] --> GT
  HC3[Human checkpoint\nOps + Safety + Personality] --> GA

  D1[Drift detector] --> RB1
  D2[Drift detector] --> RB2
  D3[Drift detector] --> RB3

  C1[Confidence threshold met] --> GS
  C2[Confidence threshold met] --> GT
  C3[Confidence threshold met] --> GA
